Log-Dispatch-Atom version 0.01

This module extends Log::Dispatch to allow logging to an Atom feed.
That feed can then be picked up by a feed reader program.

For more information on Atom, see <http://www.atomenabled.org/>.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

* XML::Atom 0.15 or later
* Log::Dispatch (any version)

